modName: The 6 Schools of Magic Symbol Resources
summary: Vector resources for the 6 schools of magic in Skyrim. Comes in .PNG, .PSD, & .ABR formats.
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/33563-3-1365283267.png[/img]

[img]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/35575-1-1367604275.jpg[/img]

[size=3]These resources are vector resources for the 6 schools of magic in Skyrim. PSDs & PNGs have resolutions of up to 10,000 pixels and @ 96 dpi, ABR (brush-type resource) have a minimum resolution of 2,500 pixels also @ 96 dpi.

All have high-quality vector edge fidelity & definition. [/size]



[/center]
